  <div class="content">
    <h1> Pro Tip</h1>
    <div id="pro-tip" style="background-color: #f1f1f1;">
      <br>
      <p>
        This week's protip <br>
        comes from <br>
        <a href="https://fedoramagazine.org/fish-a-friendly-interactive-shell/"> an article in Fedora Magazine</a>: <br>
        Alias the often-used
        <div class="code" style="text-align: center; padding-left: 0">
          ls -lhF
        </div>
        to the much faster
        <div class="code" style="text-align: center; padding-left: 0">
          ll
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>

